* installing nodejs/npm
sudo apt install nodejs
-- then somehow upgrade nodejs to 14 or any version you want

sudo npm install npm@latest -g
sudo npm install -g @angular/cli

* create project
ng new --minimal customer-manager

* start serwera i start apki w domyślnej przeglądarce
ng serve -o

* run simple typescript file
npm install -g typescript
npm install -g ts-node
ts-node ts-file.ts

* compile typescript file to javascript
tsc file.ts
